[{"id":904407,"node":"推广","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/promotions","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_mini.png?m=1658911802","description":"1 、新增支持 iMessage 功能：<br />iMessage 发送文件<br />iMessage 发送贴纸<br />iMessage 发送文本<br />iMessage 发送图文链接<br />2 、全面适配 iOS16 ，新增 12 个短信子分类。轻松自定义分类规则，高度自定义分类短信。<br />3 、每周按时更新最强机器学习模型，更加自动精准分类短信。<br />4 、iSMS/iContact 新功能的视频教程：<br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1aR4y1r7kh/?spm_id_from=333.999.0.0&amp;vd_source=0b4d473da0e181d2f3398821d6671413\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1aR4y1r7kh/?spm_id_from=333.999.0.0&amp;vd_source=0b4d473da0e181d2f3398821d6671413</a>","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/904407","replies":65,"created_ts":1671843748,"created":"09:02:28","title":"[送码！] 最强 iPhone 智能 AI 分类短信，适配 iOS16，全新改版，用户自定义分类规则，支持 iMessage！","author":"strengthen","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/strengthen","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/dfdd/2c38/543404_mini.png?m=1668644702"},{"id":904439,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"<p>第一天上午不太舒服，测了下，阳了。下午就直接发烧烧到 39 度，吃一粒洛索洛芬，退烧，这个药好像有效期 8 小时。第一天晚上又开始高烧 39 ，再吃洛索洛芬，再退烧。现在已经循环到第三天了，感觉病好遥遥无期。</p>\n<p>完全就靠退烧药吊着，身边人基本上都烧一天就好了啊</p>\n<p>时不时的还咳黄痰，不会是感染古早毒株，病毒性肺炎了吗</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/904439","replies":58,"created_ts":1671861779,"created":"14:02:59","title":"阳了之后连着三天高烧了，是不是要 G 了","author":"fan88","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/fan88","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b45b/9532/356765_mini.png?m=1667582016"},{"id":904458,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"<p>最近因为疫情好久一直在客厅刷电视剧，因为一直喜欢看农村题材的，比较下饭和热闹无需太关注剧情，依次看了《山河锦绣》和《温暖的味道》，山河主要讲扶贫，温暖更偏现代农村虽然不如前面真实，但是也挺有意思，恰好两部剧都有李乃文，还挺喜欢，大家有啥农村题材的可以推荐一下后面看</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/904458","replies":57,"created_ts":1671869443,"created":"16:10:43","title":"来推荐农村题材的剧","author":"awesomes","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/awesomes","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cb44/483e/135006_mini.png?m=1666662182"},{"id":904425,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1650127281","description":"<p>我父母都打了第三针了，他们阳了，但是都没有发烧，只是疲惫等症状，咽喉痛的程度也比较轻。而我发烧，刀片嗓，基本所有症状都占了。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/904425","replies":52,"created_ts":1671856951,"created":"12:42:31","title":"后悔没打加强针。","author":"unregister","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/unregister","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c1823de355abcada38d6f701e04de75a?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":904423,"node":"Android","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/android","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1651385965","description":"<p>估计就这三个里面选了，然后等明年降价就入手。</p>\n<p>个人需求：日常流畅度 &gt; 人像摄影 &gt; 风景摄影 &gt;&gt; 游戏需求。</p>\n<p>非富哥，在满足上面前提下想选个性价比较高的机型。</p>\n<p>请问各位数码达人们该如何选？</p>\n<p>个人没有品牌洁癖，好用就是王道。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/904423","replies":41,"created_ts":1671854709,"created":"12:05:09","title":"想换手机了， 请问下 vivoX90pro+，小米 13Pro，小米 12sUltra 怎么选？","author":"Zhancha","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Zhancha","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/50e6/b547/434804_mini.png?m=1642565999"},{"id":904499,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>感觉妙控板太贵了（京东八百多，多多 700 ）。这东西还在用老掉牙的蓝牙 3.0 ，而且延迟也不令人满意，感觉不值</p>\n<p>需要用到妙控板的唯一地方就是&lt;双指缩放&gt;，这个操作感觉一般的鼠标比较难替代。首先是不知道怎么操作鼠标才能缩放，其次操作鼠标也没法做到手指拖动这样「无极缩放」</p>\n<p>master 鼠标应该算是鼠标里面比较高端的了，我的想法是买一个 master 鼠标，这样不知道能不能解决&lt;双指缩放&gt;（首先要能缩放，其次能无极缩放）这个问题呢？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/904499","replies":36,"created_ts":1671889430,"created":"21:43:50","title":"master 鼠标能不能取代妙控板","author":"movq","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/movq","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/046c/e28c/463491_mini.png?m=1661223568"},{"id":904506,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>如题，现在还有不断的提示心率异常…\n发烧是真的难受，周围的同事朋友都阳了差不多了，还以为我是无症状。结果下午骑自行车出去买抗原回来就发烧了。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/904506","replies":32,"created_ts":1671895849,"created":"23:30:49","title":"Apple Watch 还是有点用的，突然提示心率异常，主动测一下体温，发现发烧了","author":"EminemW","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/EminemW","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/135d/bc80/413288_mini.png?m=1656078261"},{"id":904463,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>为什么不买 mac? 因为要生孩子了比较穷...</p>\n<p>需求：Java 后端开发，会开多个 docker 部署各种中间件，对游戏没需求，所以显卡无所谓。希望内存可以支持 32G ，预算 8000 左右</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/904463","replies":24,"created_ts":1671871381,"created":"16:43:01","title":"求推荐专写代码的 window 笔记本","author":"xiaofan2","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xiaofan2","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/da711b0e520e1637f0747d3d5ee0db2f?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":904445,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>今天是阳了的第八天了，身体好了，就是喉咙还是很痛，没办法好好享受美食了</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/904445","replies":24,"created_ts":1671864619,"created":"14:50:19","title":"阳了，发烧好了，但喉咙还是吞刀子一样怎么搞啊，咽部红肿有突起，有学医的 v 友知道怎么搞吗","author":"proxytoworld","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/proxytoworld","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5e55/4696/481415_mini.png?m=1651761065"},{"id":904415,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/904415","replies":24,"created_ts":1671850566,"created":"10:56:06","title":"为什么市面上看到的前端培训很多、后端培训很少？","author":"ZC3746","autho